inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let acessURL = AzureDiagnostics| where ResourceType == "APPLICATIONGATEWAYS"| where OperationName == "ApplicationGatewayAccess";
AzureDiagnostics
| where ResourceType == "APPLICATIONGATEWAYS"
| where OperationName == "ApplicationGatewayFirewall"
| where action_s == "Blocked"
| join (acessURL) on $left.clientIp_s  == $right.clientIP_s
| where TimeGenerated < TimeGenerated1 + 1m or TimeGenerated > TimeGenerated1 - 1m
| project clientIp_s , clientIP_s1, requestUri_s, Message, userAgent_s1, TimeGenerated, TimeGenerated1
| summarize count() by clientIp_s , requestUri_s, Message, userAgent_s1, bin(TimeGenerated, 1m)
| order by count_ desc 
| top 20 by count_

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
AzureDiagnostics
| where Resource == "WAFGW"
| summarize number = count() by instanceId_s, TimeGenerated
| where instanceId_s contains "role"
| extend roulenumber = extract("ApplicationGateway([a-zA-Z_a-zA-Z_0-9]*)", 1, instanceId_s) 
| project roulenumber , number , TimeGenerated
